<h1>fmtr.hpp File Reference</h1><hr><a name="_details"></a><h2>Detailed Description</h2>
Provides the fmtr class, which allows a more STL-like syntax for the formatting of input and output. 
<p>
Formatter can be considered a manipulator, or an overtaker, depending on the operator syntax you favor.<p>
